========
Quick Installation Guide:

    *) On RHEL/CentOS:

        # cd /path/to/iRedMail-x.y.z/
        # cd pkgs/
        # sh get_all.sh
        # cd ../
        # sh iRedMail.sh

    *) on Debian:

        * Install necessary packages:

            # apt-get install dialog acl dpkg-dev

        * Add mount option 'acl' in /etc/fstab which contains '/etc/' directory:

           /dev/hda1       /               ext3    acl,errors=remount-ro 0       1

        * Remount the mount point:

            # mount -o remount,rw,acl /

========
